description.raw:
* Added model: Demo Joint Types

    Model demonstrates all 8 joint types in gazebo
    The intent is to help someone learn what the joints do by seeing them in action

* Improved appearance by allowing textures to tile somewhat

* Misc fixes

    SDF 1.5 -> 1.6

    Removed <dynamics> tag from revolute2 joint
    Removed visual and collision elements from invisible weights

* Played inertia tricks to eliminate hidden weights

* uppercase -> lower case
